# Claude Agent SDK is loaded from node_modules at runtime (ESM-only,
# can't be bundled by esbuild) and ships native binaries per platform.
# We carve out just the runtime deps the SDK and its transitive imports
# need. Note: the *-{platform}-{arch} binary packages are optional deps;
# the .vsix will only contain the binary for the platform that ran
# `vsce package`. Producing a public, multi-platform release requires
# building one .vsix per (platform, arch) - see vsce docs on
# platform-specific extensions.
!node_modules/@anthropic-ai/**
!node_modules/@modelcontextprotocol/**
!node_modules/zod/**
!node_modules/zod-to-json-schema/**
